## 📁 Project Structure Analysis

### Base Structure

```
FinSense/
├── backend/              # Node.js API Server
│   ├── src/
│   │   ├── config/       # Database & logging config
│   │   ├── middleware/   # Auth, encryption, rate limiting
│   │   ├── models/       # MongoDB schemas (User, Transaction, etc.)
│   │   ├── routes/       # 8 route modules (auth, transactions, ml, etc.)
│   │   ├── services/     # 12+ business logic services
