## 🎯 Efficiency for Future Work

### Overall Assessment: ⭐⭐⭐⭐ (Very Good - 4/5)

The codebase is **well-structured and production-ready** for its current feature set, but will benefit from refactoring before significant expansion.

### Work Complexity by Feature Type

| Feature Type | Current Complexity | After Recommended Fixes |
|-------------|-------------------|------------------------|
| **Add new ML model** | 🟡 Medium (monolithic app.py) | 🟢 Easy (modular routes) |
| **Add new backend route** | 🟢 Easy (clean structure) | 🟢 Easy |
| **Add new frontend page** | 🟢 Easy (clear patterns) | 🟢 Easy |
| **Refactor ML service** | 🔴 Hard (1705-line file) | 🟢 Easy (modular) |
| **Add E2E tests** | 🟡 Medium (no framework) | 🟢 Easy (with Cypress) |
| **Deploy to production** | 🟡 Medium (manual) | 🟢 Easy (CI/CD) |

